ExtraData.ModName: CaseOh and Scott the Woz Social Links
ExtraData.ModDescription: Combines https://github.com/MrCamel999/p3rpc.sociallink.caseohmoon and https://github.com/MrCamel999/p3r.sociallink.scottwozniak into a single mod, since some BMD files are edited in both mods, making the mods slightly incompatible with one another.
